ActUnited Nations Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Implementing the United Nations Resolutions on Libya
PrecisRegulations Amending the REGULATIONS IMPLEMENTING THE UNITED NATIONS RESOLUTIONS ON LIBYA in order to bring Canada in line with its international legal obligations created by measures taken by the United Nations Security Council (UNSC) under Chapter VII of the Charter of the United Nations, namely the decisions taken by the UNSC in Resolution 2095 (2013).
